com.github.valid8j.pcond.experimentals.currying.multi

Interface MultiFunction<R>

  • Type Parameters:
    R - The type of the returned value.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Function<List<? super Object>,R>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MultiFunction.Impl

    public interface MultiFunction<R>
extends Function<List<? super Object>,R>

    An interface that represents a function that can have more than one parameters. This interface is often used in combination with Functions.curry(MultiFunction) method.
